    {
      "chinese": "當男孩到了青少年時，他們就會到聚會所學習部落的事務。到了十五歲的年齡時，部落的幹部就會帶領他們學習體能訓練、狩獵、堵河水捕魚、敬老尊賢、參加歲時祭儀及學習歌舞等。由於本身是男性，他們必須學會蓋房子、開山闢土、學習成家立業，以及在部落的聚會所，學習長輩所傳襲下來的活動及規範。",
      "ab": "Yo masakapah to ko fa’inayan a wawa^ i, itini to i soraratan ko pinanaman nangra to demak no niyaro’. Tangasa^ to i safawlima^ ko mihecaan i, misaselal to. Keriden no mama^ no kapah a misowac, mi’adop, mitafa’ to nanom a mifoting, mingodo^ to mato’asay, mikapot to ilisin, minanam to kero^ ato radiw. O fa’inayan ko tireng, saka o maminanam a misaloma’, misapala^, misaparod, ato minanam to lekakawa^ no mato’asay i soraratan no niyaro’.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2022/01/26/7271df2b61b34364171850c0118c3ea2.wav",
